  "instructions": [
    "1. Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "2. In a large bowl, combine lamb, olive oil, lemon juice, garlic, paprika, salt, and black pepper. Mix well to coat.",
    "3. Thread lamb cubes onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "4. Grill lamb kebabs for 5-7 minutes per side, or until cooked through.",
    "5. Meanwhile, brush bell peppers and onion with olive oil and season with salt and pepper.",
    "6. Grill bell peppers and onion for 3-5 minutes per side, or until tender and slightly charred.",
    "7. Serve lamb kebabs with grilled vegetables and enjoy!"
